{
  "stem": "4764.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember him saying that he didn't believe in the messiah, which I couldn't understand why everybody else did and he didn't.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other thing was that he thought the only way would be to try and escape.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he tried to influence my-- his family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, you know, you've got nothing to worry about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The messiah will come and rescue us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why should we risk our lives when we we're alive?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the penalty for escape was death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father said, there isn't such a thing as the messiah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think that had to do with the fact that wasn't as religious as-- as the others, and they didn't have that sort of-- or maybe he was more realistic.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or maybe he was more courageous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would like to think all those things, and I think he was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, it's-- the only chance that we have is to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the others didn't believe him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think that more Jews would have survived if they would have tried to escape, or if they would have tried to fight.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is why-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [DRINKS] this is why I think Israel is very important, because-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I don't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I should've done this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is why I think Israel is very important, because it's-- it's shown us that we can fight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Instead of just being taken to the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] like sheep to the slaughter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's better to fight and die, than to die like they did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I think my father was very courageous to do that, and I wouldn't be sitting here now if he hadn't done that.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
